fwprop.note:
Start Action for Commands (11,23) to delete one or more scheduling groups.
The command carries N group identifiers representing the groups to be deleted.
If N is equal to zero, then all groups currently in use must be deleted.

fwprop.entryDesc:
Load the Group ID
in data pool verFailData

Run Command Verification
Failure Procedure to generate (1,4)
report with failure code VER_SCD_ILL_G

Set action outcome to 'failure'
with failure code VER_SCD_ST_FD

fwprop.note:
This procedure generates a (1,4) report for each group identifier which is out-of-limits
which has activities associated to it (i.e. it has nOfTbaInGropu greater than zero).
The (1,4) reports are generated by the Command Verification Failure Procedure. 
The start action is declared successful as long as there is at least one group to be deleted.
